{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Tank Core&quot; is a 2D top-down shooter game infused with Roguelike elements. Players will collect various random tank components in levels, including turrets, chassis, shells, modules, and cores, to assemble unique tanks that will protect base and defeat all enemies encountered.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430070/extras/tank_1.gif?t=1736305853\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Free Combination</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By installing various collected tank components, you can create unique combat strategies. These components include turrets, chassis, shells, and modules.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430070/extras/tank_2.gif?t=1736305853\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Endless Cores</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Various cores will provide your tank with comprehensive passive bonuses, and there\u2019s no limit to the number of cores you can equip. Melt down extra turrets and bases to forge specific cores, which will retain some effects of the original components.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430070/extras/tank_3.gif?t=1736305853\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Complex Terrain</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage enemies in a variety of complex terrains where the landscape is both an obstacle and an ally. Interact with or destroy the terrain as needed.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430070/extras/tank_4.gif?t=1736305853\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build Levels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock special terrain pieces in the editor by continuall